node.detail_zh: 患者為29歲菲律賓女傭，沒有病徵，7月10日乘坐HX782號班機到港，由亞博館檢測後送院，目前在屯門醫院接受治療。
node.detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper from the Philippines. On July 10, she arrived in Hong Kong via flight HX782 and was transferred to hospital via Asia World Expo after testing. She is currently at Tuen Mun Hospital for treatment. She has no symptoms.
